            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/BLD-arbeider-for-at/Offices-and-agencies-associated-with-the-Ministry-of-Children-and-Equality/Market-Council.html?id=426149" title="">
                        Market Council
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                
                <p>The Market Council is a national authority. Its main task is to settle complaints regarding marketing. Such complaints must be handled first by the Consumer Ombudsman, the Directorate for Health and Social Affairs or the Norwegian Media Authority. Because the Market Council is an administrative organ, the Parliamentary Ombudsman for Public Administration can also review cases that the Market Council has had under consideration. The actions of the Market Council are final and can only be overridden by the ordinary courts.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    <a href="http://www.markedsradet.no/" class="externalLink" target="_blank">
                    Website of  Market Council</a>
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
