                <img src="/Upload/BLD/Etater ingress logo/SIFO.jpg" alt="SIFO
SIFO" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/BLD-arbeider-for-at/Offices-and-agencies-associated-with-the-Ministry-of-Children-and-Equality/National-Institute-for-Consumer-Research.html?id=426148" title="">
                        National Institute for Consumer Research
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                
                <p>The National Institute for Consumer Research (SIFO) is an independent, multidisciplinary centre for research, testing and reporting on consumer affairs. The institute shares its expertise with public authorities, political leaders, businesses and organizations. It conducts research for the Research Council of Norway as well as state agencies, businesses and a variety of other organizations.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    <a href="http://www.sifo.no/" class="externalLink" target="_blank">
                    Website of  National Institute for Consumer Research</a>
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
