                <img src="/Upload/BLD/Etater ingress logo/Blank.jpg" alt="blank
blank" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/BLD-arbeider-for-at/Offices-and-agencies-associated-with-the-Ministry-of-Children-and-Equality/Norwegian-Assay-Office.html?id=426152" title="">
                        Norwegian Assay Office
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                
                <p>The Norwegian Assay Office performs market surveillance and administrative duties in connection with the legally prescribed labelling of precious metals. The office monitors the quality of precious metals, ensuring that gold, silver and platinum items are labelled in accordance with the law and that information provided to consumers is both accurate and adequate.
</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
