                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/BLD-arbeider-for-at/Offices-and-agencies-associated-with-the-Ministry-of-Children-and-Equality/Norwegian-Directorate-for-Children-Youth.html?id=418035" title="">
                        Norwegian Directorate for Children, Youth and Family Affairs
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                
                <p>The task of the Norwegian Directorate for Children, Youth and Family Affairs is to provide appropriate supportive measures to children, youth and families in need of help anywhere in the country. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    <a href="http://www.bufetat.no" class="externalLink" target="_blank">
                    Website of  Norwegian Directorate for Children, Youth and Family Affairs</a>
                    
                </p>
                                 
