            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/BLD-arbeider-for-at/Offices-and-agencies-associated-with-the-Ministry-of-Children-and-Equality/The-Consumer-Dispute-Commission.html?id=426145" title="">
                        The Consumer Dispute Commission
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                
                <p>The Consumer Dispute Commission is an arbiter of conflicts, particularly those related to goods and building-trade services in which consumers (perhaps with help from the Consumer Council of Norway) have tried and failed to reach an amicable settlement. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    <a href="http://www.forbrukertvistutvalget.no/" class="externalLink" target="_blank">
                    Website of  The Consumer Dispute Commission</a>
                    
                </p>
                                 
