                        The Consumer Dispute Commission
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                
                <p>The Consumer Dispute Commission is an arbiter of conflicts, particularly those related to goods and building-trade services in which consumers (perhaps with help from the Consumer Council of Norway) have tried and failed to reach an amicable settlement.</p>
                
                
                <p>
